# Issue X3-70586 03-04-2018 by MGO: Back to back criteria in order lines inquiry - BEGIN
Subprog AM_FMI(VALEUR)
Variable Integer VALEUR
Raz [M:CCSP]FMINUMDEB, [M:CCSP]FMINUMFIN
Affzo FMINUMDEB, FMINUMFIN
End
